# CONSULT-37 ‚Äî VS light register map (D3D9 vs D3D11)

## Pipeline: who writes what

Both backends ultimately feed the **same HLSL/asm register layout** (`LightData` @ **c16**, `extendedLightData` @ **c60**), defined in `Direct3d9_VertexShaderConstantRegisters.h:28,45` and mirrored in `Direct3d11_ConstantBuffer.h:198-234`.

| Stage | D3D9 | D3D11 |
|-------|------|-------|
| Light list ‚Üí selection | `setLights` stores list (`Direct3d9_LightManager.cpp:310-313`); **`selectLights` per draw** (`Direct3d9.cpp:4012`) selects slots + accumulates ambient (`:404-418`) | **`setLights` per draw** (`ShaderPrimitiveSorter.cpp:718` ‚Üí `Direct3d11_LightManager.cpp:71`) selects slots + accumulates ambient (`:104-116`) |
| Precalc full-ambient seed | `Pass::apply` ‚Üí `setFullAmbientOn(m_fullAmbient)` (`Direct3d9_StaticShaderData.cpp:776,955`); when on, `ms_fullAmbient=(1,1,1,0)` (`Direct3d9_LightManager.h:201-208`) | **No equivalent** ‚Äî grep over `Direct3d11/**` finds zero `fullAmbient` / `setFullAmbientOn` / `containsPrecalculatedVertexLighting` |
| VS constant upload | `applyLights_vertexShader` ‚Üí `setVertexShaderConstants(VSCR_lightData, ‚Ä¶)` + `VCSR_extendedLightData` (`Direct3d9_LightManager.cpp:723-725`) | `setLights` ‚Üí `s_pixelDot3State`; **`composeSlot0Shadow`** copies into `s_slot0Shadow.lightData[]` / `extendedLightData[]` (`Direct3d11_StateCache.cpp:329-431`) |
| Material (feeds VS base term) | `setVertexShaderConstants(VSCR_material, ‚Ä¶, 5)` @ c11‚Äìc15 (`Direct3d9_StaticShaderData.cpp:862`) | `setVertexMaterialColors` @ c11,c13,c14 + `setSpecularPower` @ c15.x,c41.w (`Direct3d11_StaticShaderData.cpp:806-819`; `Direct3d11_StateCache.cpp:2448-2493`) |

**Layout reference** (from `registers.inc` in vsh-extract, matching `LightData` struct in `Direct3d9_LightManager.h:128-136`):

| Register | Field |
|----------|-------|
| **c16** | `lightData.ambient` |
| **c17‚Äìc19** | `parallelSpecular[0]` dir / diffuse / specular |
| **c20‚Äìc21** | `parallel[0]` dir / diffuse |
| **c22‚Äìc23** | `parallel[1]` dir / diffuse |
| **c24‚Äìc27** | `pointSpecular[0]` |
| **c28‚Äìc30** | `point[0]` |
| **c31‚Äìc33** | `point[1]` |
| **c34‚Äìc36** | `point[2]` |
| **c37‚Äìc39** | `point[3]` |
| **c40‚Äìc43** | `dot3` (camera, localDir+specPower, diffuse, specular) |
| **c60‚Äìc63** | `extendedLightData` back / tangent / Œîback / Œîdiffuse |

World VS final diffuse (asm path, `diffuse.inc`):

```143:144:.planning/research/vsh-extract/diffuse.inc
add r7, r7, cMaterial_emissiveColor
mov oD0, r7
```

where `r7` starts as **`vColor0`** (`c_ambient.inc:16`), then += hemispheric(c17+c60‚Äì63) + parallel(c20‚Äì23) + points + emissive(c14).

HLSL `a_simple` path (`a_simple_vs20_for_ps20.vsh:40-41`):

```40:41:.planning/research/vsh-extract/a_simple_vs20_for_ps20.vsh
	outputVertex.diffuse =  lightData.ambient.ambientColor;
	outputVertex.diffuse += calculateDiffuseLighting(true, inputVertex.position, inputVertex.normal_o);
```

which seeds from **c16**, then adds emissive(c14) + directionals.

---

## Full register table ‚Äî light-path writes only

Legend: **Z** = zero from `Zero(lightData)` / `{}`-init; **k0=1** = attenuation guard for unused point slots.

### c16 ‚Äî ambient

| | D3D9 | D3D11 |
|---|------|-------|
| **Source** | `selectLights`: `ambient = ms_fullAmbient` then `+= T_ambient color` (no intensity) (`:404-418`); uploaded `:536` | `setLights`: `cb.ambientColor += color` (no intensity, `:104-115`); snapshot `:225`; `composeSlot0Shadow` ‚Üí `lightData[0]` (`StateCache.cpp:380`) |
| **Non-precalc, list=3** | `(0,0,0,0) + ~0.13` ‚âà **(0.13,0.13,0.13,0)** | **(0.13,0.13,0.13,1.0)** ‚Äî `.w` differs (1.0 forced, `:115`) |
| **Precalc, list=0** | **`(1,1,1,0)`** (fullAmbient seed, no T_ambient in list) | **`(0,0,0,0)`** ‚Äî no seed (`setLights :76`, no `setFullAmbientOn`) |
| **Precalc, list=3** | **`(1.13,1.13,1.13,0)`** ‚âà (1,1,1)+ambient | **(0.13,0.13,0.13,1.0)** only |

**Divergence: CRITICAL for precalc** ‚Äî D3D9 always seeds white; D3D11 never does.

---

### c17‚Äìc19 ‚Äî parallelSpecular[0] (sun / dot3 diffuse-specular)

| | D3D9 | D3D11 |
|---|------|-------|
| **When filled** | Sun wins specular slot in `selectLights` (`:423-429`); `applyLights` negated world dir + colors (`:542-562`, `:639-647`) | Sun wins same cascade (`LightManager.cpp:127-138`, `:176-197`); `composeSlot0Shadow` if `d3.valid` (`StateCache.cpp:382-393`) |
| **list=0** | Z | Z (`d3.valid=false`, `:382`) |
| **list=3 (sun present)** | `-sunDir`, sun diffuse/specular | Same (negated world dir, `:391-393`) |

**Divergence: none when sun present; both zero when no directionals.**

---

### c20‚Äìc23 ‚Äî parallel[0..1] (fill + bounce ‚Äî **main VS diffuse term**)

| | D3D9 | D3D11 |
|---|------|-------|
| **Source** | Next two directionals by diffuse intensity (`selectLights :434-436`); negated dir + diffuse color (`applyLights :631-647`) | Same cascade (`LightManager.cpp:131-138`, `:199-218`); negated at fill (`StateCache.cpp:425-429`) |
| **list=0** | Z | Z |
| **list=3** | fill+bounce dirs/colors | fill+bounce dirs/colors (post 2026-06-08 fix) |

**Divergence: none (after recent fix) when directionals are in the list.**

---

### c24‚Äìc39 ‚Äî point lights

| | D3D9 | D3D11 |
|---|------|-------|
| **Filled slots** | Up to 1 spec + 4 diffuse points from list (`selectLights :442-461`, `applyLights :652-719`) | Up to 8 points packed into **LightingCB slot 3** (`LightManager.cpp:142-164`) ‚Äî **not copied into cb0 lightData** |
| **Unused attenuation** | `k0=1.0` (`:685`, `:717`) | `lightData[10/14/17/20/23].x = 1.0f` (`StateCache.cpp:444-448`) |
| **Position/color in cb0** | Written when lights selected | **Always Z** ‚Äî `composeSlot0Shadow` never fills point positions/colors |

**Divergence: HIGH if scene uses point lights in VS loop; LOW for typical outdoor building draws (no points). Attenuation guard matches.**

---

### c40‚Äìc43 ‚Äî dot3 (object-local)

| | D3D9 | D3D11 |
|---|------|-------|
| **When filled** | Only if `parallelSpecular[0]` exists (`applyLights :564-584`) | Only if `d3.valid` (`StateCache.cpp:405-408`) |
| **c41.w (spec power)** | `getSpecularPower()` (`:577`) | `ms_specularPower` from `setSpecularPower` (`:406`, `:2465`) |
| **Alpha-fade in c42.a / c43.a** | `getAlphaFadeAndBloomSettings()` (`:579-584`) | **Not patched** ‚Äî raw `d3.diffuseColor/specularColor` copied (`:407-408`) |

**Divergence: minor (alpha-fade channels); both zero when no sun.**

---

### c60‚Äìc63 ‚Äî extended hemispheric

| | D3D9 | D3D11 |
|---|------|-------|
| **When filled** | `_vsps_setExtendedLightData` when sun present (`:588-589`, `:732-759`) | `d3.backColor/tangentColor/‚Ä¶` when `d3.valid` (`StateCache.cpp:411-414`) |
| **list=0** | Z | Z |
| **list=3** | back/tangent from sun getters | Same getters (`LightManager.cpp:181-195`) |

**Divergence: none when sun present; both zero when list has no directionals.**

---

### c11‚Äìc15 ‚Äî material (not LightManager, but VS color seed)

| Register | D3D9 | D3D11 |
|----------|------|-------|
| **c11** diffuse | Pass material (`StaticShaderData.cpp:862`) | `setVertexMaterialColors` (`StateCache.cpp:2490`) |
| **c12** ambient | Uploaded with material | **Left zero** (`StateCache.cpp:2486-2488`) ‚Äî no asset VS reads it per comment |
| **c13** specular | Uploaded | `setVertexMaterialColors` |
| **c14 emissive** | Uploaded | `setVertexMaterialColors` ‚Äî **VS diffuse seed** (`inc_functions.inc:168`) |
| **c15.x spec power** | `setSpecularPower` via Pass | `setSpecularPower` (`StateCache.cpp:2463`) |

**Divergence: c12 only; likely irrelevant for world VS diffuse path.**

---

### D3D11-only: LightingCB @ **cbuffer slot 3** (320 B)

Written entirely in `setLights` (`LightManager.cpp:229-232`): ambient, one directional, up to 8 points. **Separate from cb0 slot 0.** Asset world VS reads **`cb0[16‚Ä¶]`** (slot 0), not slot 3 ‚Äî so this cbuffer is **not** the register-map target for standard world draws.

---

## Scenario diffs

### A) Precalc draw, **empty light list** (`listSz=0`)

Engine routes precalc geometry through `ms_lightsAffectingShadersWithPrecalculatedVertexLighting` (`ShaderPrimitiveSorter.cpp:1198-1199`), which can yield an empty active list (`setLights :1132-1144`).

| Register | D3D9 @ draw | D3D11 @ draw | VS impact |
|----------|-------------|--------------|-----------|
| **c16** | **(1,1,1,0)** | **(0,0,0,0)** | HLSL `a_simple`: base term **1.0 vs 0** |
| **c17‚Äìc23** | Z | Z | No dynamic parallel contribution |
| **c40‚Äìc43, c60‚Äìc63** | Z | Z | No hemispheric/dot3 |
| **c14 emissive** | material | material (if valid) | Both add emissive ‚Äî explains **‚Äúdark but not black‚Äù** if emissive > 0 |
| **vColor0** (stream) | read by asm `tfcl`/`c_simple` | D3D11 asset VS may **not declare COLOR** (handoff note; separate from register writes) | asm path: baked color still present in D3D9; may be absent in D3D11 IL |

**Where D3D11 goes to zero that D3D9 does not:** **`c16` full-ambient seed.** That is the sole light-register divergence for `listSz=0`. Everything else is either matched (k0=1 guards, zero directionals) or outside the light path (vertex stream / IL).

For **`a_simple`-style VS**: D3D9 COLOR0 ‚âà `(1,1,1) + emissive`; D3D11 ‚âà `emissive` only ‚Üí ~**emissive/1.0** brightness (dark, not black if c14 > 0).

For **asm `tfcl`**: base is **`vColor0`**, not c16 ‚Äî c16 divergence is **inert**; darkness then implicates missing COLOR stream (not a register-write gap).

---

### B) Dynamic-lit draw, **list=3** (ambient + sun + fill)

| Register | D3D9 | D3D11 | Match? |
|----------|------|-------|--------|
| **c16** | ~0.13 (non-precalc) | ~0.13 | ‚úì (after ambient intensity fix, `LightManager.cpp:104-115`) |
| **c20‚Äìc23** | fill+bounce | fill+bounce | ‚úì (post 2026-06-08 cascade + `composeSlot0Shadow :417-430`) |
| **c17‚Äìc19, c40‚Äìc43, c60‚Äìc63** | sun + hemispheric | same if `d3.valid` | ‚úì |
| **c16 precalc shaders** | **(1,1,1)+0.13** | **0.13 only** | ‚úó **8√ó floor missing** |

---

## Ranked divergences (likelihood ‚Üí black/dark output)

| Rank | Divergence | Registers | Why it darkens |
|------|------------|-----------|----------------|
| **1** | **No `setFullAmbientOn` for precalc** | **c16** | D3D9 seeds `(1,1,1,0)` before any list lights (`selectLights:404`, `setFullAmbientOn:205-208`); D3D11 never seeds (`setLights:76`). For HLSL VS using c16 as base, removes ~1.0 RGB floor. **Confirmed in source.** |
| **2** | **Empty light list on precalc draws** | c17‚Äìc23, c40‚Äìc63 all Z | Not a D3D9/D3D11 *difference* ‚Äî both zero directionals ‚Äî but combined with #1 leaves only emissive. Explains dark-not-black when c14 > 0. |
| **3** | **Point lights not mapped into cb0** | c24‚Äìc39 | D3D11 leaves positions/colors zero; only k0 guard matches. Irrelevant for outdoor walls, critical for point-lit interiors. |
| **4** | **Dot3 alpha-fade `.w` channels not mirrored** | c42.a, c43.a | D3D9 patches fade/bloom (`applyLights:581-584`); D3D11 copies raw colors (`StateCache:407-408`). Unlikely primary wall darkness. |
| **5** | **Ambient `.w` channel** | c16.w | D3D9 leaves 0; D3D11 forces 1.0 (`LightManager:115`). Only matters if VS reads `.w`. |
| **6** | **No `setObeysLightScale` in D3D11** | all light colors | D3D9 toggles scaled vs raw getters (`Direct3d9_LightManager.cpp:318-339`); D3D11 always uses `getScaledDiffuseColor()`. Secondary. |

